title: Blood Brothers
description:
Blood Brothers

Based on a true story about a notorious murder in Baarn in 1961. 16-year-old Simon befriends the wealthy van Riebeeck brothers and spends time in their magnificent home. The three agree to hide Ronnie, a petty criminal on the run, in their attic. But before long, Ronnie becomes a burden to them. Nominated for the Golden Calf at the Nederlands Film Festival, 2008. Directed by Arno Dierickx and stars Erik van Heijningen, Matthijs van de Sande Bakhuyzen and Derk Stenvers. 

In Dutch, English subtitles
